
For employees who have not been through the PRC/PEP process before, please be 
advised that there will be PRC/ PEP training available.  Please attend one of 
the training sessions below: 

PRC/PEP Employee & Supervisor Training

Date: October 30,2000
Place: Hyatt, Aboretum
Session I: 9:00- 11:00 a.m.
Session II: 2:00- 4:00 p.m.

Date: October 31,2000
Place: EB49C3
Session I: 9:00- 11:00 a.m.
Session II: 2:00- 4:00 p.m.

In the next few days, all employees will receive PRC/PEP training material in 
the mail.  If you have utilized the PEP system before, then attendance for 
the training sessions are optional.  The new intranet interface should make 
the PEP system more user friendly and faster.  

Please contact Jennifer Jordan at ext: 3-7554, if you have any questions 
concerning training materials or classes